Package com.aleozlx.pacswitch

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PacswitchAPI
    The platform independent pacswitch service client API, which is used to facilitate WAN connections by communicating with a pacswitch server, thereby user data are switched so as to pass NAT routers both ways.
